{"arkId":"cl010338067","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010338067","modified ":"2025-11-03","title":"lampe \u00e0 la grenouille","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"lampe \u00e0 la grenouille"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : \u00e9poque romaine (IIIe - IVe s. av. J.-C.) (-30 - 395)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-30,"endYear":395,"imprecision":"","text":"\u00e9poque romaine","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"ME 172","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"D.890.1.30","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"},{"value":"272","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s \u00e9gyptiennes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cette lampe est form\u00e9e de deux \u00e9l\u00e9ments : la partie principale est un r\u00e9servoir \u00e0 huile presque circulaire et tr\u00e8s aplati fait de deux moiti\u00e9s pos\u00e9es l\u0027une sur l\u0027autre et soud\u00e9es. Le dessus est perc\u00e9 en son milieu d\u0027un trou destin\u00e9 au remplissage et autour duquel est moul\u00e9 le d\u00e9cor. Sur cette partie se greffe le bec de la lampe, perc\u00e9 \u00e0 son extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 d\u0027un orifice pour la m\u00e8che. Le d\u00e9cor de l\u0027objet \u00e9voque le corps d\u0027une grenouille : on distingue les pattes repli\u00e9es \u00e0 l\u0027arri\u00e8re et, de chaque c\u00f4t\u00e9 de l\u0027ouverture centrale du corps, un quadrillage incis\u00e9 est cens\u00e9 figurer l\u0027aspect granuleux d\u0027une peau de batracien. Ce d\u00e9cor se poursuit sur le col qui repr\u00e9sente le cou et la t\u00eate de l\u0027animal.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","